<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_kʼanʒol" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>kʼanʒol</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>камзол</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>camisole</q></cit></sense><etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>камзол</w></mentioned>. Последнее — через <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>Kamisol</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fr"><lang/><w>саmisole</w></mentioned> — к <mentioned xml:lang="it"><lang/><w>camiciola</w><gloss><q>фуфайка</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/><gloss><q>майка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/><gloss><q>кофточка</q></gloss></mentioned>,  (уменьшительное к %icamicia%i ‘рубашка’). Сюда же <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/><w>qoanzolg</w><gloss><q>короткий бешмет</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>камзол</w></mentioned>. The latter was borrowed through <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>Kamisol</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fr"><lang/><w>саmisole</w></mentioned> — to <mentioned xml:lang="it"><lang/><w>camiciola</w><gloss><q>jersey</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/><gloss><q>undershirt</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/><gloss><q>blouse</q></gloss></mentioned>,  (a diminutive form of %icamicia%i ‘shirt’). <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/><w>qoanzolg</w><gloss><q>short beshmet</q></gloss></mentioned> is related to it as well.</etym></entry>